I"~<p>smallest unit of concurrency that I can think of, with more detail:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wrapper {
    var mutable flag
    CALL λ₁
    CLR flag
loop:
    TEST flag
    BRNZ exit
    CALL λ₂
    BR loop
exit:
    CALL λ₃
}
</code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>λ₁ - begin
λ₂ - message handler
λ₃ - finish
</code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>λ₁ (self, &amp;rest args)
λ₂ (self, message)
λ₃ (self)
</code></pre></div></div>

